        "text_tEa3z5ePz0LAemzN": "<p>Need a watch that can survive your job site?</p>",
        "text_VuRL1zZTPTaW8l7N": "<p>Frustrated by watches that can&apos;t handle extreme weather?</p>",
        "text_TmgOs58wvaSzLypy": "<p>Worried about breaking your watch while working or adventuring?</p>",
